as surprised as you.

561
00:29:14,410 --> 00:29:16,390
Just like when you
first returned to the country,

562
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,599
Liangliang came to see me

563
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,559
and said you should get some rest

564
00:29:20,559 --> 00:29:22,000
and not participate in any projects.

565
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,640
She cares so much about you.

566
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:24,799
You mustn't

567
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,559
let that girl down.

568
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,440
Muran?

569
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,799
What's wrong? You look unhappy.

570
00:29:49,599 --> 00:29:50,319
Don't you have

571
00:29:50,319 --> 00:29:51,480
anything to explain to me?

572
00:29:52,599 --> 00:29:53,599
Explain what?

573
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:58,119
Did you tell Mr. Jiang

574
00:29:58,720 --> 00:29:59,960
to let me rest

575
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:01,279
and not let me join any projects?

576
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:08,440
Muran,

577
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,640
don't obsess over doing projects.

578
00:30:10,759 --> 00:30:12,359
Methods for making big money

579
00:30:12,359 --> 00:30:14,240
can't be shown in public.

580
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,160
Didn't the last

581
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,640
collaboration go well?

582
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,960
We're in the same boat.

583
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:22,079
I protect you, you protect me.

584
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,720
We achieve success together.

585
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,480
I'm just being kind.

586
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,480
Kind, huh?

587
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,950
You used my grandmother
to return to Lysen.

588
00:30:34,119 --> 00:30:36,160
Don't think I don't know
what you're planning.

589
00:30:36,359 --> 00:30:36,880
Also,

590
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,359
I'm warning you for the last time,

591
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:40,160
I am the one named Bai.

592
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,640
Grandmother loves you
the most, of course.

593
00:30:45,559 --> 00:30:46,359
But,

594
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,240
how do you know

595
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,839
this isn't Grandmother's wish?

596
00:30:59,759 --> 00:31:00,559
Hello, Mr. Bai.

597
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:02,880
Mr. Bai.

598
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,039
Mom.

599
00:31:04,039 --> 00:31:04,559
Welcome back.

600
00:31:04,559 --> 00:31:05,359
Where are you going?

601
00:31:07,010 --> 00:31:09,200
Since when do you have to take out
the trash yourself?

602
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,200
What are you all doing?

603
00:31:11,559 --> 00:31:12,599
Don't play dumb with me!

604
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:14,160
Why does the Bai family even employ you?

605
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:16,500
Since when does my mom have
to take out the trash herself?

606
00:31:17,039 --> 00:31:17,839
Stop shouting.

607
00:31:18,519 --> 00:31:20,079
This has nothing to do with them.

608
00:31:20,519 --> 00:31:21,480
This is the dregs

609
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,470
of the traditional Chinese medicine
your grandmother drank.

610
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:26,480
I heard that you can't just throw
these medicine dregs away.

611
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:28,559
The daughter-in-law
must bury them herself

612
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:29,890
to cure the illness at its root.

613
00:31:31,279 --> 00:31:32,799
Go on. Go see your grandmother.

614
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:42,720
Grandmother.

615
00:31:43,039 --> 00:31:44,000
Muran.

616
00:31:44,559 --> 00:31:45,599
Why didn't you tell me

617
00:31:45,599 --> 00:31:47,240
you were coming back?

618
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,359
I could have had the kitchen

619
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:51,240
prepare something delicious for you.

620
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:54,599
Grandmother, regarding Bai Liangliang's
return to the company,

621
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:56,390
you were the one
who approached Mr. Jiang, right?

622
00:32:00,700 --> 00:32:02,440
You knew that I went out
to gain experience

623
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:05,150
specifically so I could come back
and ask Jiang Dongchao for a position.

624
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,440
Why won't even you support me?

625
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:08,079
Why would you help an outsider instead?

626
00:32:09,799 --> 00:32:10,599
Muran.

627
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,160
Do you remember what

628
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,559
I told you before?

629
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:19,359
Come.

630
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,759
Come here.

631
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:22,720
Come here.

632
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:32,200
Your mother doesn't understand business

633
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:34,279
and can't make any decisions.

634
00:32:34,519 --> 00:32:36,279
Every decision I make

635
00:32:37,039 --> 00:32:38,390
is for the sake of the Bai family.

636
00:32:40,559 --> 00:32:42,720
Did you think your grandfather's brothers

637
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,160
were so peaceful?

638
00:32:46,839 --> 00:32:47,799
All these years,

639
00:32:48,519 --> 00:32:49,799
I have been able to keep

640
00:32:49,799 --> 00:32:52,240
the Bai family firmly in my own hands.

641
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:53,759
We didn't end up like Lysen,

642
00:32:53,759 --> 00:32:55,519
being controlled by outsiders.

643
00:32:55,519 --> 00:32:56,640
And why was that?

644
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,200
It was all for you.

645
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:05,079
Jiang Dongchao and Bai Liangliang
can afford to make mistakes,

646
00:33:06,279 --> 00:33:08,079
but you cannot.

647
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:13,640
So, according to what you're saying,
at Lysen,

648
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:15,079
I can only be an idle person?

649
00:33:15,079 --> 00:33:16,319
To the outside world, am I just

650
00:33:16,319 --> 00:33:17,799
a mascot for the Bai family?

651
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:23,960
You only need to execute

652
00:33:25,759 --> 00:33:27,119
whatever decision I make.

653
00:33:27,839 --> 00:33:29,920
Staying there honestly

654
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:32,079
and letting others
stir up trouble for you,

655
00:33:32,079 --> 00:33:32,880
isn't that good?

656
00:33:36,559 --> 00:33:37,319
Your mother

657
00:33:37,319 --> 00:33:38,839
can't help you with anything.

658
00:33:39,839 --> 00:33:41,920
Without my support for the two of you,

659
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:44,799
how could you compete
with those old guys in the Bai family?

660
00:33:47,079 --> 00:33:49,079
Just be a wealthy boy.

661
00:33:50,279 --> 00:33:52,279
Stay out of other matters.

662
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:07,960
(Bai Muran,)

663
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,719
(you think of yourself
as an unappreciated talent,)

664
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:14,320
(but in reality, you are an insignificant)

665
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:16,039
(discarded pawn to everyone.)

666
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,559
(Now,)

667
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,480
(I'm going to turn this discarded pawn)

668
00:34:22,239 --> 00:34:23,920
(into my temporary ally.)

669
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,800
(A fake ally,)

670
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:30,400
(but a real tool.)

671
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,599
Let's meet up.

672
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:42,719
Tomorrow at 8:00 PM.

673
00:34:44,119 --> 00:34:45,600
Come to Chongguangli to pick me up.

674
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,719
Off work?

675
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,440
You really are quite free.

676
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,679
Is taking you home
considered being free?

677
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:15,519
How long do you plan on doing this?

678
00:35:16,719 --> 00:35:17,719
Until

679
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:20,199
you get used to me taking you home.

680
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,760
Let's go.

681
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,199
But I have an appointment today.

682
00:35:25,239 --> 00:35:26,119
That's fine.

683
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,039
I'll just walk with you.

684
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,280
I've arrived.

685
00:35:48,639 --> 00:35:49,480
Cheer up a bit.

686
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:54,239
After walking with
your head down for so long,

687
00:35:54,239 --> 00:35:55,159
you should also learn

688
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:57,039
to look up once in a while

689
00:35:57,039 --> 00:35:58,360
at this different world.

690
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:01,199
Perhaps it isn't as bad

691
00:36:01,199 --> 00:36:02,159
as we imagined.

692
00:36:09,639 --> 00:36:10,639
If it were possible

693
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:13,320
for someone

694
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,800
to face all of this with you

695
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,440
and protect you,

696
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,760
would you...

697
00:36:23,199 --> 00:36:24,159
Would you be willing?

698
00:36:24,159 --> 00:36:29,580
♪Oh, but sadly I'm only a friend♪

699
00:36:29,580 --> 00:36:35,620
♪You the moonlight of my soul♪

700
00:36:38,119 --> 00:36:40,039
I'm used to being alone.

701
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,360
Then just think about it.

702
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:49,599
Whether as a teammate

703
00:36:49,599 --> 00:36:50,519
or something else,

704
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,119
as long as I can be by your side.

705
00:37:03,719 --> 00:37:04,790
Someone's waiting for you.

706
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:06,440
I have things to do.

707
00:37:06,599 --> 00:37:07,519
I'll head off first.

708
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,719
It's fine.

709
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,500
Now that I've brought you here,

710
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:11,960
my job is done.

711
00:37:21,159 --> 00:37:21,960
Chen Mo.

712
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:29,320
I am not the person

713
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,679
who can stay by your side.

714
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:31,900
=Episode 10=
(The Discarded Pawn)

715
00:38:32,580 --> 00:38:35,020
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

716
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:41,220
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

717
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:45,180
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

718
00:38:45,180 --> 00:38:49,700
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

719
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:57,220
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

720
00:38:57,220 --> 00:39:01,140
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

721
00:39:01,140 --> 00:39:05,180
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

722
00:39:05,180 --> 00:39:08,700
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

723
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:12,660
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

724
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:16,820
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

725
00:39:16,820 --> 00:39:21,020
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

726
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:24,820
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

727
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:28,900
♪Keep walking through the light♪

728
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:33,100
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

729
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:39,420
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

730
00:39:56,540 --> 00:40:03,180
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

731
00:40:03,180 --> 00:40:07,020
♪An apology that came too late♪

732
00:40:07,020 --> 00:40:11,660
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

733
00:40:11,740 --> 00:40:19,140
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

734
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:23,220
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

735
00:40:23,220 --> 00:40:27,300
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

736
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:31,300
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

737
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:35,060
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

738
00:40:35,060 --> 00:40:39,260
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

739
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:43,420
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

740
00:40:43,420 --> 00:40:47,140
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

741
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:51,180
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

742
00:40:51,180 --> 00:40:55,220
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

743
00:40:55,220 --> 00:41:01,420
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
